3.3. ADHD VBM analysis
Individuals with ADHD exhibited decreased GMV in the bilateral 
OFC (extending to the bilateral ACC), right putamen (extending to the 
right superior temporal gyrus [STG]), left inferior frontal gyrus (IFG), 
SFG, ACC/ mPFC, and precentral gyrus compared to NCs (see Table 2
and 
for details). No regions of increased GMV were found in the 
Fig. 2
current meta-analysis.
