2.2. Study selection
This meta-analysis included studies that satised the following 
conditions. (1) Individuals were diagnosed as having ADHD according to 
the Diagnostic and Statistical Manual of Mental Disorders, Fourth or 
Fifth Edition (DSM-4 or 5) or International Classication of Diseases 
(ICD-10); (2) The resting-state functional imaging and GMV of in-
dividuals with ADHD and NCs were compared at voxel-wise level; (3) 
The study was published in a peer-reviewed English or Chinese-language 
